    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "他将我儿当猪狗",
        "何必上殿去斗口",
        "儿虽死孙已长忠臣有后",
        "创业君哪一个思念故旧",
        "到如今干戈息音信无有",
        "当日誓言出你口",
        "当日里荥阳城功劳少有",
        "忘却荥阳将你救",
        "怎忍胸中气一口",
        "我劝伯母且罢手",
        "纪夫人",
        "纪子",
        "纪母",
        "越思越气难忍受",
        "那项羽中巧计汉王逃走",
        "随何"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（纪夫人、纪子同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪夫人",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大节凛冰霜，抚孤子，奉养高堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "婆婆万福！"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。坐下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见祖母！"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。\n媳妇！自你丈夫在荥阳替主赴难，随何有信也曾言道，汉王发下誓愿，母受鸿\n恩，子食俸禄，至今未受半点恩荣。从前还可说是干戈未息，无暇及此；如今\n天下已定，为何不见恩诏，莫非汉王食言乎？"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿观汉王，鹰顾狼视，可与共患难，不可与共富贵。况我家薄有良田，尚堪度\n日；当日伤心之事，婆婆提它作甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗐！儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "坐草堂未开言痛心疾首，\n想起了纪信儿珠泪双流。\n舍性命替君难楚营去投。\n他临行发誓愿必有报酬。\n因何故加恩诏不下龙楼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "当日里荥阳城功劳少有、那项羽中巧计汉王逃走、到如今干戈息音信无有、纪夫人",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老婆母休得要双眉紧皱，\n年迈人禁不住万种忧愁。\n我家中尚温饱薄有田畴。\n到后来飞鸟尽良弓必收。"
        },
        {
          "character": "儿虽死孙已长忠臣有后、创业君哪一个思念故旧、纪母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但愿得老天爷多多保佑，\n一家人守田园快乐无忧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（随何上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "随何",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怒气不息向前走，\n见了伯母说原由。"
        },
        {
          "character": "随何",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伯母在上，侄儿拜揖。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤侄少礼。落坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "随何",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢坐。\n啊，嫂嫂！"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叔叔！"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤侄公事勤劳，何暇至此？"
        },
        {
          "character": "随何",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小侄今日为一事前来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为了何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "随何",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现今天下大定，汉王正位，大封功臣，小侄等皆已封侯赐爵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有功必赏，真乃有道明君！"
        },
        {
          "character": "随何",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说什么有道明君，据侄看来是无道昏君！"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此话怎讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "随何",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伯母！想当日我兄长替君赴难之后，小侄有信前来，言道：汉王发下誓愿，富\n贵同享，以酬救主之功。伯母可记得否？"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个……"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "以往之事提它作甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "随何",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伯母、嫂嫂有所不知。昨日汉王大宴功臣，萧何奏请汉王，要追封我兄救驾之\n功。那汉王反说：假扮天子大逆不道，就该问斩，既然人死，也不深究；功不\n掩罪，断无封侯之理！"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪母",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "婆婆醒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪母",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "闻此言气得我浑身乱抖，"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好昏君！"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大骂昏王礼不周。\n我儿替死一命休。\n反而无情恩作仇。\n即刻上殿辩理由。"
        },
        {
          "character": "忘却荥阳将你救、当日誓言出你口、越思越气难忍受、纪夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "母亲年高六十九，\n好似风烛泪双流。\n争此虚名不如休。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何必上殿去斗口、随何",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "汉王威权真少有，\n一言不合斩人头。\n怕得是此去命难留。"
        },
        {
          "character": "我劝伯母且罢手、纪母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "人生不过百年寿，\n忠义名儿万古留。\n死后尚且不封侯。\n拼着老命闯龙楼。\n随何带路快快走！"
        },
        {
          "character": "他将我儿当猪狗、怎忍胸中气一口、纪夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲去不得！"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "儿等不必苦攀留。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（纪母下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叔叔保护随娘后，"
        },
        {
          "character": "随何",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "嫂嫂放心谅无忧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（随何下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "纪夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "此去吉凶猜不透，\n手掩柴扉泪双流。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（纪夫人拉纪子同下。）"
        }
      ],
